OL,3,CMinister admits poor behaviour could
OL,4,Cbe widespread across health service
OL,6,FThey included allegations of an
OL,7,Fintolerable working environment and a
OL,8,Fpattern of consistently poor behaviour
OL,9,Fwithin the unit.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, Health Committee chairman
OL,12,FPhilip McGuigan asked the minister
OL,13,Fwhen committee members and the public
OL,14,Fwould see the report.
OL,16,FMr Nesbitt said he was taking legal
OL,17,Fadvice over whether it could be placed
OL,18,Fin the Assembly library, adding he
OL,19,Fneeded to be careful about not
OL,20,Fprovoking legal action by identifying
OL,21,Findividuals.
