OL,3,CMinister admits poor behaviour could
OL,4,Cbe widespread across health service
OL,6,FHe said: "It was a devastating report,
OL,7,Fa very bad culture was allowed to
OL,8,Fdevelop and that demonstrated itself
OL,9,Fin behaviours and in the fact that
OL,10,Fthere was a terrible breakdown in
OL,11,Frelationships with one surgeon walking
OL,12,Finto the building and others walking
OL,13,Fout and saying they were working from
OL,14,Fhome."
OL,16,FHe said he had written to the chairman
OL,17,Fof the Belfast Health and Social Care
OL,18,FTrust and would meet him on Friday.
