OL,6,FHe added: "I would say the language
OL,7,Fthat was used in that letter was
OL,8,Frobust, to say the least."
OL,10,FThe minister also pointed out that the
OL,11,Freport had concluded that the cardiac
OL,12,Funit was clinically safe.
