OL,3,CMinister admits poor behaviour could
OL,4,Cbe widespread across health service
OL,6,FMr McGuigan said: "Rows, abuse,
OL,7,Fbullying of junior staff by more
OL,8,Fsenior staff, surgeons not coming to
OL,9,Fwork, throwing of medical instruments
OL,10,Fduring operations, one consultant
OL,11,Fallegedly being told that if a patient
OL,12,Fdies 'I will tell the family it is
OL,13,Fyour fault', behaviour putting
OL,14,Fpatients at risk of harm and
OL,15,Freportedly, when staff made complaints
OL,16,Fto the Belfast trust, the result was
OL,17,Fextremely slow to be investigated.
OL,19,F"This is what has been reported as
OL,20,Fbeing in the report. It is shocking
OL,21,Fand extremely concerning."
