OL,3,CMinister admits poor behaviour could
OL,4,Cbe widespread across health service
OL,6,FHe said the public needed to see the
OL,7,Frecommendations of the report to be
OL,8,F"assured of their confidence in this
OL,9,Flife-saving unit of one of our
OL,10,Fhospitals".
OL,12,FMr Nesbitt responded: "I accept if I
OL,13,Fam due to go for a procedure tomorrow,
OL,14,Fnext week, next month I am now looking
OL,15,Fat it differently than I would have
OL,16,Fdone before reports of this report
OL,17,Fwere in the public domain."
OL,19,FHe added: "I cannot look you in the
OL,20,Feye and say this unit is an outlier.
