OL,3,CMinister admits poor behaviour could
OL,4,Cbe widespread across health service
OL,6,F"This was a cultural issue. It would
OL,7,Fnot surprise me if cultural issues
OL,8,Fexisted in other units within our arms-
OL,9,Flength bodies, including those five
OL,10,Fgeographically defined trusts.
OL,12,F"Sometimes when something like this
OL,13,Fcomes into the public domain, it
OL,14,Feffectively gives permission to other
OL,15,Fpeople in other units to become
OL,16,Fwhistleblowers.
OL,18,F"We are on standby for that
OL,19,Feventuality without any knowledge that
OL,20,Fit is coming but which logic says is
OL,21,Fhighly possible."
